{"tid":1634443,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一芳香港被誤會撐中遭「裝飾」　市民今主動清潔還原","createTime":"2019-10-07T08:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T12:27:29.000Z","uid":2036,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d86d5a0f52a79dec8c983e66a3f381745892d7b2","tid":1634443,"uid":2036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:00:56.000Z","msg":"真手足定自己友都好, 起碼有改善,係POSITIVE NOISE<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%80%E8%8A%B3%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%A2%AB%E8%AA%A4%E6%9C%83%E6%92%90%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%AD-%E8%A3%9D%E9%A3%BE-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E4%BB%8A%E4%B8%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E9%82%84%E5%8E%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%258A%25B3%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2592%2590%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2581%25AD-%25E8%25A3%259D%25E9%25A3%25BE-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25BB%258A%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25BD%2594%25E9%2582%2584%25E5%258E%259F%2F&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSnxVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=021058be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%258A%25B3%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2592%2590%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%2581%25AD-%25E8%25A3%259D%25E9%25A3%25BE-%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25BB%258A%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25BD%2594%25E9%2582%2584%25E5%258E%259F%2F&h=60237576\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%80%E8%8A%B3%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%A2%AB%E8%AA%A4%E6%9C%83%E6%92%90%E4%B8%AD%E9%81%AD-%E8%A3%9D%E9%A3%BE-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E4%BB%8A%E4%B8%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%B8%85%E6%BD%94%E9%82%84%E5%8E%9F/</a><br />\n<br />\n在 8 月 5 日香港「三罷」期間，一芳台灣水果茶總公司的大陸微博和微信曾經發表反罷工言論，令香港網民不滿和抵制，甚至波及了一直尊重示威者的香港總代理，影響持續至今。不過香港總代理負責人劉心暉說，收到相片顯示有市民今早到一芳店舖清潔，令他感嘆「香港人真係好可愛」。<br />\n<br />\n從劉心暉的 Facebook 專頁可見，有市民今早帶備鐵梯和清潔工具，清洗鐵閘和招牌的塗鴉字句。原本被寫成「共芳」的一芳招牌，亦因為市民重新塗上白漆而回復原貌。<br />\n<br />\n反送中示威浪潮當中，網民曾經在 8 月 5 日發起「三罷」，部分一芳香港店舖在 8 月 5 日當日罷工，引起了一芳注意，一芳當時在微博和微信發文指「一芳堅決支持一國兩制」，「強烈譴責並堅決反對暴力罷工」。<br />\n<br />\n後來一芳香港總代理說，台灣一芳立場，與香港總代理旗下所有一芳店立場無關。香港總代理並且尊重本港各店的立場。其後，亦有網民和一芳香港員工力撐香港總代理支持香港示威者。"},{"pid":"ecf52aa704bbd298eaf90c55a570910978f5a8b0","tid":1634443,"uid":57621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:26:24.000Z","msg":"感謝幫手清潔手足"},{"pid":"dc9aa87154e75049667086ada824d81729e28e52","tid":1634443,"uid":48060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ecf52aa704bbd298eaf90c55a570910978f5a8b0","tid":1634443,"uid":57621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:26:24.000Z","msg":"感謝幫手清潔手足"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:27:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92bd171fb573a9ac0359a34cd0fda414e45eb11d","tid":1634443,"uid":46822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:28:30.000Z","msg":"抵讚<br />\n錫春袋先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09226d2c08d1d20ba6adfffb4c4e238d093dc55","tid":1634443,"uid":108997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:30:49.000Z","msg":"手足多謝曬"},{"pid":"2a2b8498ac65a4607d543654b3039f23f2328043","tid":1634443,"uid":295650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92bd171fb573a9ac0359a34cd0fda414e45eb11d","tid":1634443,"uid":46822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:28:30.000Z","msg":"抵讚<br />\n錫春袋先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:31:20.000Z","msg":"錫錫"},{"pid":"fe43a31853e5d94e62807b161cf97f7430d124ac","tid":1634443,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:31:35.000Z","msg":"多謝手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=